issues.body:
The term "entity" could refer to many things.

In the specified ASN.1, a `PkixEvidence` has a `ClaimDescriptionTbs` which has multiple `ReportedEntity`, each of which has a type and multiple attributes. We could replace "entity" with "claim":

```
PkixEvidence ::= SEQUENCE {
    tbs        ClaimDescriptionTbs,
    signatures SEQUENCE SIZE (0..MAX) of SignatureBlock
}

ClaimDescriptionTbs ::= SEQUENCE {
    version        INTEGER,
    reportedClaims SEQUENCE SIZE (1..MAX) OF ReportedClaim
}

ReportedClaim ::= SEQUENCE {
    claimType          OBJECT IDENTIFIER,
    reportedAttributes SEQUENCE SIZE (1..MAX) OF ReportedAttribute
}
```
